                        >> AND keep in mind you have to meet both conditions of having enoughs 0's and 1's
                            i.e. neither can be negative
                >> just max (1) and (2) to get the maxForm
            >> Since we need row-1 at each iteration then we need an unnamed dummy row. It cannot be "" because this would
