After writing the recursive code memoisation isn't a big task!
```
1. Make a global 3-D array with m, n and index as it's dimentions.
2. Set every element of the array as -1 using memset function.
3. Check if stored the value is not equal to -1 and return the value as we've already calculated it.
4. Store the values in the 3-D array. 
5. Return the last element of the 3-D array.
